  reviewCornerSpawn: {fileID: 1135736044}
  examiner: {fileID: 195455184}
  lines:
    approach: Hold on! You can't enter the lab just yet. What would you like to do
      today?
    labTour: Lab Tour it is! Roam freely and try the tools and reagents. Come back
      to me when you want to take on a campaign.
    campaignExplain: The Campaign takes you through the class periods. Pass every
      experiment with 90% or better to unlock the next. Ready to pick your episode?
    episodePrompt: Which episode will it be?
    lockedEpisode: "That episode is still locked \u2014 clear the earlier ones first!"
    coatPrompt: Safety first! Put on your lab coat at the locker before we begin.
    readyPrompt: All geared up! Are you prepared to begin?
    thresholdWarn: The period will start as soon as you walk in. Step through when
      you're ready!
    congrats: Congratulations! You handled that experiment brilliantly. Let's head
      back outside.
    supplyWarn: "Oh no \u2014 there isn't enough reagent left to finish the experiment.
      We'll have to restart the period."
    welcome: Welcome to the lab! I'm Pharmee. Come talk to me at the door whenever
      you're ready to begin.
  lineSeconds: 5.5
